<lb n="0821a18" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead>佛說呵雕阿那<note n="0821009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鋡＝含【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0821009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鋡＝含【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0821009"><lem wit="【大】">鋡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">含</rdg></app>經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0821a19" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0821a20" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">東晉<note n="0821010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天竺三藏＝西域沙門【三】【宮】</note><note n="0821010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天竺三藏＝西域沙門【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0821010"><lem wit="【大】">天竺三藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">西域沙門</rdg></app>竺曇無蘭譯</byline>
<lb n="0821a21" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT14p0821a2101">聞如是：</p><p xml:id="pT14p0821a2104" rend="inline">一時，佛在舍衛國祇陀<note n="0821011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">恒＝園【三】【宮】</note><note n="0821011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">恒＝園【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0821011"><lem wit="【大】">恒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">園</rdg></app>，呵雕阿那
<lb n="0821a22" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0821009"><lem wit="【大】">鋡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">含</rdg></app>將五百優婆塞至舍利弗所，作禮已却
<lb n="0821a23" ed="T"/>坐。舍利弗為說經，大歡喜而退。復至佛所，以
<lb n="0821a24" ed="T"/>頭面著地，叉手繞佛三匝却坐。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0821a2413" rend="inline">佛問呵雕阿
<lb n="0821a25" ed="T"/>那<app type="star" corresp="#0821009"><lem wit="【大】">鋡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">含</rdg></app>：「若有何功德，教化五百弟子隨<note n="0821012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">從＝侍【三】【宮】</note><note n="0821012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">從＝侍【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0821012"><lem wit="【大】">從</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">侍</rdg></app>
<lb n="0821a26" ed="T"/>汝？」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0821a2602" rend="inline">呵雕阿那<app type="star" corresp="#0821009"><lem wit="【大】">鋡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">含</rdg></app>即長跪叉手言：「我常奉行
<lb n="0821a27" ed="T"/>佛所說四事。何等為四？一者、布施於人；二
<lb n="0821a28" ed="T"/>者、說善說；三者、<note n="0821013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">瞻＝占【三】【宮】</note><note n="0821013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">瞻＝占【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0821013"><lem wit="【大】">瞻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">占</rdg></app>視同學給足有無；四者、
<lb n="0821a29" ed="T"/>同學者財共不計。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0821a2908" rend="inline">佛言：「善哉！善哉！已過去
<pb n="0821b" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0538.0821b"/>
<lb n="0821b01" ed="T"/>佛，無有過是四事；未來佛亦無有過是四事；
<lb n="0821b02" ed="T"/>今現在佛，亦無有過是四事。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0821b0212" rend="inline">佛為呵雕阿那
<lb n="0821b03" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0821009"><lem wit="【大】">鋡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">含</rdg></app>說經已，各大歡喜而退。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0821b0311" rend="inline">呵雕阿那<app type="star" corresp="#0821009"><lem wit="【大】">鋡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">含</rdg></app>還
<lb n="0821b04" ed="T"/>歸入<note n="0821014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">舍＝含【明】</note><app n="0821014"><lem wit="【大】">舍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">含</rdg></app>，呼諸人<note n="0821015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">客＝容【聖】</note><app n="0821015"><lem wit="【大】">客</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">容</rdg></app>奴婢坐著前，好為說經
<lb n="0821b05" ed="T"/>開解，語生死善惡之道；復上殿呼諸<note n="0821016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">持＝侍【聖】</note><app n="0821016"><lem wit="【大】">持</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">侍</rdg></app>藏
<lb n="0821b06" ed="T"/>人、諸<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha CBETA.say" wit="【CBETA】【麗】">妓<note type="cf1">KI20n0834_p1169b19</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">伎</rdg></app>女著前，為說經<note n="0821017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">戒＝誡【聖】＊</note><app n="0821017"><lem wit="【大】">戒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">誡</rdg></app>，皆大歡喜；復上
<lb n="0821b07" ed="T"/>後殿，為諸夫人婦女，說經<app type="star" corresp="#0821017"><lem wit="【大】">戒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">誡</rdg></app>已訖，還至正
<lb n="0821b08" ed="T"/>殿，齋戒床上，端<note n="0821018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">坐＝正【宮】</note><app n="0821018"><lem wit="【大】">坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">正</rdg></app>定意，便得等心。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0821b0814" rend="inline">第一
<lb n="0821b09" ed="T"/>天上四王請諸天皆會坐，共稱譽呵雕阿那
<lb n="0821b10" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0821009"><lem wit="【大】">鋡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">含</rdg></app>功德，<note n="0821019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">四天＝天四【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0821019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">四天＝天四【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0821019"><lem wit="【大】">四天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">天四</rdg></app>王中尊王下至呵雕阿那<app type="star" corresp="#0821009"><lem wit="【大】">鋡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">含</rdg></app>
<lb n="0821b11" ed="T"/>舍，面稱譽呵雕阿那<app type="star" corresp="#0821009"><lem wit="【大】">鋡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">含</rdg></app>功德。呵雕阿那<app type="star" corresp="#0821009"><lem wit="【大】">鋡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">含</rdg></app>
<lb n="0821b12" ed="T"/>時得等心，不答天王。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0821b1209" rend="inline">佛邊有一比丘，至呵
<lb n="0821b13" ed="T"/>雕阿那<app type="star" corresp="#0821009"><lem wit="【大】">鋡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">含</rdg></app>舍，呵雕阿那<app type="star" corresp="#0821009"><lem wit="【大】">鋡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">含</rdg></app>起迎比丘前坐，
<lb n="0821b14" ed="T"/>比丘說言：「佛坐中常相稱譽功德。」呵雕阿那
<lb n="0821b15" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0821009"><lem wit="【大】">鋡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">含</rdg></app>問比丘言：「佛稱譽我時，邊有白衣無？」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0821b1516" rend="inline">比
<lb n="0821b16" ed="T"/>丘言：「無有白衣，正使有白衣，<note n="0821020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔有〕－【聖】</note><app n="0821020"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>何等嫌疑
<lb n="0821b17" ed="T"/><note n="0821021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">那＝耶【三】【宮】，邪【聖】</note><note n="0821021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">那＝耶【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【麗-CB】【CB】，＝邪【聖】</note><app n="0821021"><lem resp="CBETA.maha CBETA.say" wit="【CBETA】【麗】">耶<note type="cf1">KI20n0834_p1169c10</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">那</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">耶</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">邪</rdg></app>？」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0821b1702" rend="inline">呵雕阿那<app type="star" corresp="#0821009"><lem wit="【大】">鋡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">含</rdg></app>言：「佛語至誠，恐白衣不
<lb n="0821b18" ed="T"/>信者，便當墮泥犁中；正使信佛語者，便復
<lb n="0821b19" ed="T"/>來承事我，布施我，我不喜煩擾於人，<note n="0821022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝於【明】</note><app n="0821022"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">於</rdg></app>是
<lb n="0821b20" ed="T"/>故問耳。」比丘辭去。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0821b2008" rend="inline">呵雕阿那<app type="star" corresp="#0821009"><lem wit="【大】">鋡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">含</rdg></app>言：「想朝來
<lb n="0821b21" ed="T"/>未食，且留飲食。」便行澡水，下<note n="0821023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飯＝飲【三】【宮】</note><note n="0821023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飯＝飲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0821023"><lem wit="【大】">飯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">飲</rdg></app>食訖。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0821b2115" rend="inline">比丘
<lb n="0821b22" ed="T"/>還白佛言：「屬至呵雕阿那<app type="star" corresp="#0821009"><lem wit="【大】">鋡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">含</rdg></app>舍，道說言：『佛
<lb n="0821b23" ed="T"/>坐中大相稱譽。』呵雕阿那<app type="star" corresp="#0821009"><lem wit="【大】">鋡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">含</rdg></app>因問我言：『佛稱
<lb n="0821b24" ed="T"/>譽我時，邊有白衣無？』我言：『無白衣，正使有白
<lb n="0821b25" ed="T"/>衣有何等嫌疑？』呵雕阿那<app type="star" corresp="#0821009"><lem wit="【大】">鋡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">含</rdg></app>言：『佛稱譽我，
<lb n="0821b26" ed="T"/>實至誠不妄，白衣不信佛語者，便當墮泥犁
<lb n="0821b27" ed="T"/>中；正使信者，便復來承事我，我不喜煩擾
<lb n="0821b28" ed="T"/>他人，以是故問耳。』」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0821b2808" rend="inline">佛言：「善哉！善哉！我不常
<lb n="0821b29" ed="T"/>為汝曹說呵雕阿那<app type="star" corresp="#0821009"><lem wit="【大】">鋡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">含</rdg></app>有七事，今復益一事
<pb n="0821c" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0538.0821c"/>
<lb n="0821c01" ed="T"/>為八事。何等為八事？一者、不求不欲令人知；
<lb n="0821c02" ed="T"/>二者、信不欲令人知；三者、自羞不欲令人知；
<lb n="0821c03" ed="T"/>四者、自慚不欲令人知；五者、精進不欲令人
<lb n="0821c04" ed="T"/>知；六者、自觀不欲令人知；七者、得禪不欲令
<lb n="0821c05" ed="T"/>人知；八者、黠慧不欲令人知。所以不欲令人
<lb n="0821c06" ed="T"/>知者，不欲煩擾於人，故不欲令人知。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0821c0615" rend="inline">佛說
<lb n="0821c07" ed="T"/>經已，諸比丘皆大歡喜，起前為佛作禮。<note n="0821024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">光明皇后願文【聖】</note></p></cb:div>
<lb n="0821c08" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><note n="0821025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【聖】</note><app n="0821025"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>呵雕阿那<app type="star" corresp="#0821009"><lem wit="【大】">鋡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">含</rdg></app><note n="0821026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（一卷）【聖】</note><app n="0821026"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">經一卷</rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
